static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2670533\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 28, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vgl1677562561657.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vgl1677562561657.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vgl1677562561657.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vgl1677562561657\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">EnableDevTools</code> is an HTML widget property that allows a user to enable\n\t\tthe DevTools (Developer Tools) of Chromium Embedded Framework (CEF). </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vgl1677562561657__section_w304ab1b5b1_w305ab1b5_w306ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\">EnableDevTools = <cite class=\"cite\">True/False</cite>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The default value of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">EnableDevTools</span> property is\n\t\t\t\t\t<cite class=\"cite\">False</cite>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">If you want to enable the DevTools of CEF, then you must set the\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">EnableDevTools</span> property in the .INI file to <cite class=\"cite\">True</cite>\n\t\t\t\tas follows:</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">[widgets] HTML=uhtml(EnableDevTools=true)</span>\n</p>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vgl1677562561657__table_o3h_gpt_qwb\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"vgl1677562561657__table_o3h_gpt_qwb__entry__1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Value</strong></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"vgl1677562561657__table_o3h_gpt_qwb__entry__2\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Description</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"vgl1677562561657__table_o3h_gpt_qwb__entry__1\"><cite class=\"cite\">true/false</cite></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"vgl1677562561657__table_o3h_gpt_qwb__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The setting in the .INI file can be overruled by setting the property either\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdeclaratively in the definitions of a HTML widget field or\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tin the code by using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span>. The latter approach\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\talso allows a user to enable or disable the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">EnableDevTools</code> selectively in a code\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\twhen required. The property needs to be set before the HTML\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\twidget is initialized at the start of a component. The users\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tmust restart the component in case the value of the property\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tis changed for a HTML widget (or widgets). </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"vgl1677562561657__note_sbl_vcr_qwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">EnableDevTools</span> property is\n\t\t\t\t\tignored or disabled in case a component is compiled with\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/nodebug</span>.</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vgl1677562561657__section_pvb_dqt_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d291436e144\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vgl1677562561657__rxf1665703074477_table_d12119e1_d12120e1_d12121e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vgl1677562561657__section_osp_lqt_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d291436e175\">Setting the Property</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">To set this, specify it in the HTML widget definition in the initialization file. </p>\n<p class=\"p\">For example: HTML=uhtml(EnableDevTools=true)</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vgl1677562561657__section_xns_3rt_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d291436e187\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ied1665702642247.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ied1665702642247.html\" title=\"The uhtml widget is a field-level widget in a form component that renders HTML code (including HTML, CSS, and JavaScript) or displays a web page (when the field value is a URL prefixed by an ampersand (&amp;www.mysite.com/doc/index.html). Uniface provides a logical widget called HTML, which is mapped to uhtml.\">uhtml (HTML Widget)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrz1665702655781.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/nodebug</a><p>Instruct Uniface to compile the application shell, component, or global ProcScript so that it cannot be debugged.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ied1665702642247.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uhtml (HTML Widget)</a><p>The uhtml widget is a field-level widget in a form component that renders HTML code (including HTML, CSS, and JavaScript) or displays a web page (when the field value is a URL prefixed by an ampersand (&amp;www.mysite.com/doc/index.html). Uniface provides a logical widget called HTML, which is mapped to uhtml.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wbc1665702642322.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>DebugPort</a><p>Specify a port number that can be used by MSAA-based tools to connect to the widget for testing purposes.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2670533\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2670533\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "EnableDevTools (HTML Widget) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 28, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 EnableDevTools is an HTML widget property that allows a user to enable the DevTools (Developer Tools) of Chromium Embedded Framework (CEF). EnableDevTools = True/False The default value of the EnableDevTools property is False . If you want to enable the DevTools of CEF, then you must set the EnableDevTools property in the .INI file to True as follows: [widgets] HTML=uhtml(EnableDevTools=true) Value Description true/false The setting in the .INI file can be overruled by setting the property either declaratively in the definitions of a HTML widget field or in the code by using $properties or $fieldproperties . The latter approach also allows a user to enable or disable the EnableDevTools selectively in a code when required. The property needs to be set before the HTML widget is initialized at the start of a component. The users must restart the component in case the value of the property is changed for a HTML widget (or widgets). Note: The EnableDevTools property is ignored or disabled in case a component is compiled with /nodebug . Usage Dynamic? No Setting the Property To set this, specify it in the HTML widget definition in the initialization file. For example: HTML=uhtml(EnableDevTools=true) Applies To uhtml (HTML Widget) Related Links /nodebug Instruct Uniface to compile the application shell, component, or global ProcScript so that it cannot be debugged. uhtml (HTML Widget) The uhtml widget is a field-level widget in a form component that renders HTML code (including HTML, CSS, and JavaScript) or displays a web page (when the field value is a URL prefixed by an ampersand (&www.mysite.com/doc/index.html). Uniface provides a logical widget called HTML, which is mapped to uhtml. DebugPort Specify a port number that can be used by MSAA-based tools to connect to the widget for testing purposes. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}